                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10264" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1538</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">304 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">葫芦娃药业：可转债发行二次被否</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Huluwa Pharmaceutical: The issuance of convertible bonds was rejected for the second time</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘胜强 ，蒲红艳，刘钟薇，刘妮娜，陈逢文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海南葫芦娃药业集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新“国九条” 可转债 ；葫芦娃药业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New “Nine National Regulations” ， Convertible Bonds,  Huluwa P-armaceutical</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着资本市场监管力度持续加强，上市公司在融资过程中面临的合规要求日趋严格。2023年全国医药领域开展的反腐集中整治，进一步反映了这一趋势。在此背景下，本案例聚焦海南葫芦娃药业集团股份有限公司（简称“葫芦娃药业”），全面梳理其可转换公司债券（简称“可转债”）发行申请接连被否的全过程。可转债发行申请被否本身较为罕见，而葫芦娃药业更是新“国九条”实施后首家可转债发行申请遭否决的上市公司。通过本案例的学习，学生可在掌握可转债基本理论的同时，深入思考此次发行申请被否背后的深层原因，并识别企业在融资过程中可能存在的治理短板与合规风险。此外，该案例对那些虽希望通过融资实现发展，却游走在监管边缘、试图寻求“捷径”的企业也具有重要警示意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous strengthening of capital market regulation, listed companies face increasingly strict compliance requirements in financing. The 2023 nationwide concentrated anti-corruption campaign in the pharmaceutical industry further reflects this trend. This case focuses on Hainan Huluwa Pharmaceutical Group Co., Ltd. (referred to as &quot;Huluwa Pharmaceutical&quot;), comprehensively reviewing the successive rejections of its convertible corporate bond issuance applications. Such rejection is relatively rare, and Huluwa Pharmaceutical is the first listed company rejected after the implementation of the new &quot;National Nine Measures&quot;. Through this case study, students can not only master the basic theory of convertible bonds, but also deeply explore the underlying reasons for the rejection, and identify governance weaknesses and compliance risks in the enterprise’s financing process. In addition, this case serves as an important warning for companies that aim to develop through refinancing but are on the edge of regulation and seek shortcuts.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《公司理财》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业融资方式；可转债；企业会计准则；企业治理；信息披露；财务管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
